  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そこまで騎士になりたいなら
上官に君の事を推薦してみるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you want to become a knight that much, I can put
in a recommendation for you to my superior officer.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>素質は十分みたいだからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You seem to have quite the potential.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>本当に！？　ありがとう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really?! Thank you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれよ！
騎士って、忙しいんじゃねぇのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wa-Wait a second here!
Aren't knights busy people?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それは当然だ。
命令とあらば、どんなときでも
どんな場所にでも出向くのが仕事だからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course we are. If we receive an order,
it's our job to go anywhere at any time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ無理だ。
そんな事してたら
毎日狩りをする時間がなくなっちまう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then this sure isn't happening. If I did that,
I wouldn't have any time to hunt every day.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに言ってるのよ、リッド！
騎士になれるんだよ？
もう狩りなんてしなくていいんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck are you saying, Reid?!
You could become a knight.
You wouldn't have to hunt anymore.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オレが狩りやめたら
村の年寄りや身体の弱い連中に
誰が肉を届けてやれるんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I stop hunting, who's gonna deliver meat to the
elderly folks and the folks with weaker
constitutions in the village?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ……そうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah... Good point.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
